вҖӘIs that why you treat us like this?
вҖӘBecause I chose to stay in Soweto.

389
00:18:19.291 --> 00:18:21.375
вҖӘWhile others got
вҖӘa better life in the suburbs.

390
00:18:21.458 --> 00:18:23.500
вҖӘNow you're looking down on me and my kids?

391
