вҖӘ-You don't need to say it.

393
00:18:27.125 --> 00:18:30.458
вҖӘWhat does Matipa and her kids have
вҖӘthat's different from myself and Sarah?

394
00:18:31.041 --> 00:18:32.833
вҖӘJonasi. I know when you look at me.

395
00:18:32.916 --> 00:18:35.750
вҖӘI'm a reminder of your past
вҖӘthat you're trying to run away from.

396
00:18:35.833 --> 00:18:37.041
вҖӘSomething you look down on.

397
00:18:37.125 --> 00:18:40.208
вҖӘIf that's the case. just know
вҖӘthat you and I come from the same place.

398
00:18:40.291 --> 00:18:41.500
вҖӘno matter how much you look down on me.

399
00:18:41.583 --> 00:18:43.916
вҖӘ-You're talking shit.
вҖӘ-You're full of shit. Fuck off!

400
00:18:44.500 --> 00:18:46.291
вҖӘAnd I'm done being your toilet!

